body:
Hello Chris,



I am trying to find out why I get those unrealistically high cooling loads for a building in NY. From what I can find online the usual cooling load in NY is around 6-10% of total thermal loads.



Maybe something I do wrong when I assign materials, zones? or something with my setting points or natural ventilation ?



Thank you very much in advance,



Dimitris
